26
00:02:39,657 --> 00:02:42,381
I have a bad knee, which I do have at the moment.

27
00:02:42,401 --> 00:02:44,462
And I have a headache, things like that.

28
00:02:47,306 --> 00:02:49,868
So the suffering comes from a relationship to the body.

29
00:02:49,889 --> 00:02:51,770
The body can only offer us pain.

30
00:02:52,087 --> 00:02:56,073
and pleasure, of course.

31
