The Buddha, of course, made this mistake in his training.

32
00:03:00,679 --> 00:03:13,133
After he had achieved all these jhana states, absorption states, in the first part of his training for about two years or so, he then went into the process of self-mortification.

33
00:03:13,153 --> 00:03:20,543
