35
00:03:23,437 --> 00:03:26,639
So there was this process of eating less and less and less.

36
00:03:27,561 --> 00:03:38,031
This seemingly was the doctrine of the Jain leader, where the saint is one who finally just stops eating, just lets go.

37
00:03:40,612 --> 00:03:48,099
So he found that to be just more pain and he left it highly disappointed and very thin.

38
00:03:49,092 --> 00:03:55,019
And that's when he went off to sit under the tree where he became fully liberated.

39
00:03:55,379 --> 00:04:16,365
So somewhere along that line, moving away from self-mortifications and reflecting upon his practice, he came upon the insight into what was really causing the problem, really causing the suffering and the escape from suffering.

40
00:04:16,632 --> 00:04:18,233
